itable\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n|-\n|align=center style=\"color:#cccccc;\" colspan=4|NH / Not held || means an event was not held.\n|-\n|align=center style=\"color:#cccccc;\" colspan=4|MR / Minor-ranking event || means an event is/was a minor-ranking event.\n|-\n|align=center style=\"color:#cccccc;\" colspan=4|NR / Non-ranking event || means an event is/was no longer a ranking event.\n|-\n|align=center style=\"color:#cccccc;\" colspan=4|R / Ranking event|| means an event is/was now a ranking event\n|}\n{{reflist|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n==Career finals==\n===Pro-am finals: 1 (1 runner-up)===\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n|width=\"80\"|'''Outcome'''\n|width=\"20\"|'''No.'''\n|width=\"50\"|'''Year'''\n| style=\"width:250px;\"|'''Championship'''\n| style=\"width:200px;\"|'''Opponent in the final'''\n| style=\"width:100px;\"|'''Score'''\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ffa07a;\"|Runner-up \n| 1.\n| [[Cue sports at the 2017 Asian Indoor and Martial Arts Games#Snooker singles|2017]]\n| [[Asian Indoor and Martial Arts Games]]\n| {{flagicon|CHN}} {{sortname|Zhao|Xintong}}\n| 2\u20134\n|}\n\n===Amateur finals: 2 (2 titles)===\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n|-\n|width=\"80\"|'''Outcome'''\n|width=\"20\"|'''No.'''\n|width=\"50\"|'''Year'''\n| style=\"width:250px;\"|'''Championship'''\n| style=\"width:200px;\"|'''Opponent in the final'''\n| style=\"width:100px;\"|'''Score'''\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner\n| 1.\n| 2011\n| {{nowrap|[[IBSF World Snooker Championship|World Amateur Snooker Championship]]}}\n| {{flagicon|WAL}} {{sortname|Lee|Walker}}\n| 10\u20139\n|-\n| style=\"background:#98fb98;\"|Winner\n| 2.\n| 2014\n| {{nowrap|[[IBSF World Under-21 Snooker Championship|World Amateur Under-21 Snooker Championship]]}}\n| {{flagicon|IRL}} {{sort|Boileau|[[Josh Boileau]]}}\n| 8\u20133\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.worldsnooker.com/players/hossein-vafaei-ayouri/ Hossein Vafaei] at ''worldsnooker.com''\n* \n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Vafaei, Hossein}}\n[[Category:Iranian snooker players]]\n[[Category:People from Abadan, Iran]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Cue sports players at the 2010 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Asian Games competitors for Iran]]\n", "name_user": "Lee Vilenski", "label": "safe", "comment": "cleanup - fix season links usingWP:AWB", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hossein_Vafaei"}
